{% doc %}
  @prompt
    Create a clean, premium ingredient spotlight section for a sleep supplement brand called Ariya. The section should feel modern, soft, trustworthy, and science-backed, while still warm and easy to understand.
    
    Section goal
    Show the ingredients inside Calm Nights in a visually appealing grid that highlights what each ingredient does. This section should communicate transparency, quality, and function.
    
    Brand style
    Use Ariya brand colors only:
    
    Deep purple: #3C0E66
    Gold: #EFCB21
    Light purple: #C99CF1
    Do not use navy blue or off-brand colors.
    
    Section header
    Headline: Inside Calm Nights
    Subheadline: Every ingredient was chosen for a reason. No proprietary blends. No hidden doses.
    
    Layout
    Create a grid of ingredient cards
    Desktop: 3 cards per row
    Mobile: 2 cards per row
    Keep spacing clean and balanced
    Section background should be a very light soft gray or off-white
    Cards should have a white background, soft rounded corners, subtle border or shadow, and a clean premium feel
    Very important image instructions
    The ingredient visuals should not look like flat square photos inside a frame.
    
    Instead:
    
    Each ingredient image should appear like a cut-out / isolated ingredient
    It should look like the actual ingredient is floating naturally
    Use transparent PNG-style presentation if possible
    No circular crop
    No icon badge style
    No image inside a circle
    No generic framed stock-photo look
    The ingredient should be the main visual, centered near the top of each card, with breathing room around it
    A subtle floating look is ideal
    Card structure
    Each ingredient card should include:
    
    Small rounded purple label/tag above the ingredient name
    Ingredient name in bold
    Short benefit description underneath
    Ingredient cards content
    1. Tag: CALM MIND
    Ingredient: L-Theanine
    Description: Supports relaxation and helps quiet racing thoughts before bed.
    
    2. Tag: STRESS RELIEF
    Ingredient: Lemon Balm Extract
    Description: Traditional botanical used to promote calmness and support relaxation.
    
    3. Tag: RELAXATION
    Ingredient: Chamomile Extract
    Description: Well-known herbal extract traditionally used to support restful sleep.
    
    4. Tag: DEEP CALM
    Ingredient: Magnolia Bark Extract
    Description: Supports relaxation and helps ease mental tension before bed.
    
    5. Tag: SLEEP SUPPORT
    Ingredient: L-Tryptophan
    Description: Amino acid that helps support your body’s natural melatonin and serotonin production.
    
    6. Tag: SLEEP PATHWAYS
    Ingredient: Vitamin B6
    Description: Supports neurotransmitter production involved in healthy sleep cycles.
    
    7. Tag: SLEEP QUALITY
    Ingredient: Tart Cherry Extract
    Description: Naturally contains compounds that support healthy sleep quality and recovery.
    
    Typography
    Headline should feel strong and clean
    Ingredient names should stand out clearly
    Keep descriptions readable and slightly smaller
    Make the purple category tags bold and easy to scan
    Overall feel should be premium, minimal, and not cluttered
    Design rules
    Keep the design elegant and simple
    Make it easy to skim
    Use soft shadows and rounded corners
    Make the cards feel polished and high-converting
    Prioritize mobile responsiveness
    Do not overcrowd the section
    Keep visual emphasis on the ingredient cutout and benefit
    Final instruction
    Build this as a polished Shopify section that looks custom and premium, with ingredient images that feel like floating real ingredients, not boxed-in photos.
    
    One important note for you
    If you want Shopify to actually make the images feel like floating ingredients, your best move is to upload transparent PNG cutouts of each ingredient.
    Because if you upload normal square images, Shopify will usually just place them as square images., make the images float up and down 
{% enddoc %}
{% assign ai_gen_id = block.id | replace: '_', '' | downcase %}

{% style %}
  .ai-ingredient-spotlight-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.section_background }};
    padding: {{ block.settings.section_padding_top }}px 20px {{ block.settings.section_padding_bottom }}px;
  }

  .ai-ingredient-spotlight__container-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .ai-ingredient-spotlight__header-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: {{ block.settings.header_spacing }}px;
  }

  .ai-ingredient-spotlight__headline-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.headline_size }}px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: {{ block.settings.headline_color }};
    margin: 0 0 12px;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .ai-ingredient-spotlight__subheadline-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.subheadline_size }}px;
    color: {{ block.settings.subheadline_color }};
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.5;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  .ai-ingredient-spotlight__grid-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: {{ block.settings.card_gap }}px;
    margin-top: {{ block.settings.grid_top_spacing }}px;
  }

  .ai-ingredient-spotlight__card-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    background-color: {{ block.settings.card_background }};
    border-radius: {{ block.settings.card_border_radius }}px;
    padding: {{ block.settings.card_padding }}px;
    text-align: center;
    {% if block.settings.card_border_style == 'solid' %}
      border: {{ block.settings.card_border_width }}px solid {{ block.settings.card_border_color }};
    {% endif %}
    {% if block.settings.card_shadow_enabled %}
      box-shadow: 0 {{ block.settings.card_shadow_y }}px {{ block.settings.card_shadow_blur }}px {{ block.settings.card_shadow_spread }}px {{ block.settings.card_shadow_color }};
    {% endif %}
    transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
  }

  .ai-ingredient-spotlight__card-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover {
    {% if block.settings.card_hover_lift %}
      transform: translateY(-4px);
    {% endif %}
    {% if block.settings.card_shadow_enabled and block.settings.card_hover_lift %}
      box-shadow: 0 {{ block.settings.card_shadow_y | plus: 4 }}px {{ block.settings.card_shadow_blur | plus: 4 }}px {{ block.settings.card_shadow_spread }}px {{ block.settings.card_shadow_color }};
    {% endif %}
  }

  .ai-ingredient-spotlight__image-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 100%;
    height: {{ block.settings.image_height }}px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-bottom: {{ block.settings.image_bottom_spacing }}px;
    position: relative;
  }

  .ai-ingredient-spotlight__image-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    max-width: 100%;
    max-height: 100%;
    width: auto;
    height: auto;
    object-fit: contain;
    {% if block.settings.float_animation_enabled %}
      animation: ai-ingredient-float-{{ ai_gen_id }} {{ block.settings.float_duration }}s ease-in-out infinite;
    {% endif %}
  }

  .ai-ingredient-spotlight__placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background-color: #f4f4f4;
    border-radius: 8px;
  }

  .ai-ingredient-spotlight__placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }} svg {
    width: 60%;
    height: 60%;
    opacity: 0.3;
  }

  {% if block.settings.float_animation_enabled %}
    @keyframes ai-ingredient-float-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      0%, 100% {
        transform: translateY(0px);
      }
      50% {
        transform: translateY(-{{ block.settings.float_distance }}px);
      }
    }

    .ai-ingredient-spotlight__card-{{ ai_gen_id }}:nth-child(1) .ai-ingredient-spotlight__image-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      animation-delay: 0s;
    }

    .ai-ingredient-spotlight__card-{{ ai_gen_id }}:nth-child(2) .ai-ingredient-spotlight__image-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      animation-delay: 0.2s;
    }

    .ai-ingredient-spotlight__card-{{ ai_gen_id }}:nth-child(3) .ai-ingredient-spotlight__image-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      animation-delay: 0.4s;
    }

    .ai-ingredient-spotlight__card-{{ ai_gen_id }}:nth-child(4) .ai-ingredient-spotlight__image-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      animation-delay: 0.6s;
    }

    .ai-ingredient-spotlight__card-{{ ai_gen_id }}:nth-child(5) .ai-ingredient-spotlight__image-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      animation-delay: 0.8s;
    }

    .ai-ingredient-spotlight__card-{{ ai_gen_id }}:nth-child(6) .ai-ingredient-spotlight__image-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      animation-delay: 1s;
    }

    .ai-ingredient-spotlight__card-{{ ai_gen_id }}:nth-child(7) .ai-ingredient-spotlight__image-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      animation-delay: 1.2s;
    }
  {% endif %}

  .ai-ingredient-spotlight__tag-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: inline-block;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.tag_background }};
    color: {{ block.settings.tag_text_color }};
    font-size: {{ block.settings.tag_font_size }}px;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    padding: {{ block.settings.tag_padding_vertical }}px {{ block.settings.tag_padding_horizontal }}px;
    border-radius: {{ block.settings.tag_border_radius }}px;
    margin-bottom: {{ block.settings.tag_bottom_spacing }}px;
  }

  .ai-ingredient-spotlight__name-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.ingredient_name_size }}px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: {{ block.settings.ingredient_name_color }};
    margin: 0 0 {{ block.settings.name_bottom_spacing }}px;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .ai-ingredient-spotlight__description-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.description_size }}px;
    color: {{ block.settings.description_color }};
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin: 0;
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 749px) {
    .ai-ingredient-spotlight-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      padding: {{ block.settings.section_padding_top | times: 0.7 }}px 16px {{ block.settings.section_padding_bottom | times: 0.7 }}px;
    }

    .ai-ingredient-spotlight__headline-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.headline_size | times: 0.7 }}px;
    }

    .ai-ingredient-spotlight__subheadline-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.subheadline_size | times: 0.9 }}px;
    }

    .ai-ingredient-spotlight__grid-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      gap: {{ block.settings.card_gap | times: 0.7 }}px;
    }

    .ai-ingredient-spotlight__card-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      padding: {{ block.settings.card_padding | times: 0.8 }}px;
    }

    .ai-ingredient-spotlight__image-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      height: {{ block.settings.image_height | times: 0.8 }}px;
    }

    .ai-ingredient-spotlight__tag-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.tag_font_size | times: 0.9 }}px;
    }

    .ai-ingredient-spotlight__name-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.ingredient_name_size | times: 0.9 }}px;
    }

    .ai-ingredient-spotlight__description-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.description_size | times: 0.9 }}px;
    }
  }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .ai-ingredient-spotlight__image-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      animation: none;
    }
  }
{% endstyle %}

<div class="ai-ingredient-spotlight-{{ ai_gen_id }}" {{ block.shopify_attributes }}>
  <div class="ai-ingredient-spotlight__container-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
    <div class="ai-ingredient-spotlight__header-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
      <h2 class="ai-ingredient-spotlight__headline-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.headline }}</h2>
      <p class="ai-ingredient-spotlight__subheadline-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.subheadline }}</p>
    </div>

    <div class="ai-ingredient-spotlight__grid-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
      {% for i in (1..7) %}
        {% liquid
          assign tag_key = 'ingredient_' | append: i | append: '_tag'
          assign name_key = 'ingredient_' | append: i | append: '_name'
          assign description_key = 'ingredient_' | append: i | append: '_description'
          assign image_key = 'ingredient_' | append: i | append: '_image'

          assign tag = block.settings[tag_key]
          assign name = block.settings[name_key]
          assign description = block.settings[description_key]
          assign image = block.settings[image_key]
        %}

        <div class="ai-ingredient-spotlight__card-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
          <div class="ai-ingredient-spotlight__image-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            {% if image %}
              <img
                src="{{ image | image_url: width: 400 }}"
                alt="{{ name | escape }}"
                loading="lazy"
                width="400"
                height="400"
                class="ai-ingredient-spotlight__image-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
              >
            {% else %}
              <div class="ai-ingredient-spotlight__placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                {{ 'product-1' | placeholder_svg_tag }}
              </div>
            {% endif %}
          </div>

          <div class="ai-ingredient-spotlight__tag-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ tag }}</div>
          <h3 class="ai-ingredient-spotlight__name-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ name }}</h3>
          <p class="ai-ingredient-spotlight__description-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ description }}</p>
        </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

